<!--  
Dynamic Slideshow with Sideswipe Gradient mask transitions. 

Variable Explanations:

'timer' :: after next image is finished loading number of seconds 
		between transition

'fadetime' :: velocity of image crossfade. Increment for faster fades, 
		decrement for slower. Approximately equal to seconds.
                NEEDS TO BE LOWER THAN 'timer' VALUE
		
'xcord' :: x coordinates of top left corner of slideshow images

'ycord' :: y coordinates of top left corner of slideshow images

'swipevis' :: 1 or 0, if set to 1 the low alpha swipes will be visible

'swipealp'  ::  alpha setting of the swipes

'linkson'  ::  1 or 0, if set to 1 images will serve as buttons
		  that will redirect to designated link
-->




